  "an9.36:7.2": "In the same way, take a mendicant who enters and remains in the dimension of infinite space. … ",
  "an9.36:7.3": "",
  "an9.36:7.4": "",
  "an9.36:7.5": "‘The dimension of infinite space is a basis for ending the defilements.’ ",
  "an9.36:7.6": "That’s what I said, and this is why I said it. ",
  "an9.36:8.1": "‘The dimension of infinite consciousness is a basis for ending the defilements.’ … ",
  "an9.36:8.2": "‘The dimension of nothingness is a basis for ending the defilements.’ ",
  "an9.36:8.3": "That’s what I said, but why did I say it? ",
